[
    {
        "index": 1,
        "start_time": 7192,
        "end_time": 9181,
        "text": "All animals communicate."
    },
    {
        "index": 2,
        "start_time": 9181,
        "end_time": 12645,
        "text": "Crabs wave their claws at each other\nto signal that they&#39;re healthy"
    },
    {
        "index": 3,
        "start_time": 12645,
        "end_time": 13964,
        "text": "and ready to mate."
    },
    {
        "index": 4,
        "start_time": 13964,
        "end_time": 17468,
        "text": "Cuttlefish use pigmented skin cells\ncalled chromatophores"
    },
    {
        "index": 5,
        "start_time": 17468,
        "end_time": 21556,
        "text": "to create patterns on their skin\nthat act as camouflage"
    },
    {
        "index": 6,
        "start_time": 21556,
        "end_time": 23476,
        "text": "or warnings to rivals."
    },
    {
        "index": 7,
        "start_time": 23476,
        "end_time": 25889,
        "text": "Honeybees perform complex dances"
    },
    {
        "index": 8,
        "start_time": 25889,
        "end_time": 31061,
        "text": "to let other bees know the location\nand quality of a food source."
    },
    {
        "index": 9,
        "start_time": 31061,
        "end_time": 34889,
        "text": "All of these animals have impressive\ncommunication systems,"
    },
    {
        "index": 10,
        "start_time": 34889,
        "end_time": 37266,
        "text": "but do they have language?"
    },
    {
        "index": 11,
        "start_time": 37266,
        "end_time": 38555,
        "text": "To answer that question,"
    },
    {
        "index": 12,
        "start_time": 38555,
        "end_time": 43052,
        "text": "we can look at four specific qualities\nthat are often associated with language:"
    },
    {
        "index": 13,
        "start_time": 43052,
        "end_time": 44232,
        "text": "discreteness,"
    },
    {
        "index": 14,
        "start_time": 44232,
        "end_time": 46356,
        "text": "grammar,"
    },
    {
        "index": 15,
        "start_time": 46356,
        "end_time": 48054,
        "text": "productivity,"
    },
    {
        "index": 16,
        "start_time": 48054,
        "end_time": 50180,
        "text": "and displacement."
    },
    {
        "index": 17,
        "start_time": 50180,
        "end_time": 53330,
        "text": "Discreteness means that there is a set\nof individual units,"
    },
    {
        "index": 18,
        "start_time": 53330,
        "end_time": 55473,
        "text": "such as sounds or words,"
    },
    {
        "index": 19,
        "start_time": 55473,
        "end_time": 59044,
        "text": "that can be combined\nto communicate new ideas,"
    },
    {
        "index": 20,
        "start_time": 59044,
        "end_time": 62158,
        "text": "like a set of refrigerator poetry magnets\nyou can rearrange"
    },
    {
        "index": 21,
        "start_time": 62158,
        "end_time": 64506,
        "text": "to create different phrases."
    },
    {
        "index": 22,
        "start_time": 64506,
        "end_time": 66433,
        "text": "Grammar provides a system of rules"
    },
    {
        "index": 23,
        "start_time": 66433,
        "end_time": 69841,
        "text": "that tells you how to combine \nthose individual units."
    },
    {
        "index": 24,
        "start_time": 69841,
        "end_time": 72954,
        "text": "Productivity is the ability \nto use language"
    },
    {
        "index": 25,
        "start_time": 72954,
        "end_time": 76942,
        "text": "to create an infinite number of messages."
    },
    {
        "index": 26,
        "start_time": 76942,
        "end_time": 79798,
        "text": "And displacement is the ability \nto talk about things"
    },
    {
        "index": 27,
        "start_time": 79798,
        "end_time": 81722,
        "text": "that aren&#39;t right in front of you,"
    },
    {
        "index": 28,
        "start_time": 81722,
        "end_time": 85809,
        "text": "such as past, future, or fictional events."
    },
    {
        "index": 29,
        "start_time": 85809,
        "end_time": 90045,
        "text": "So, does animal communication exhibit \nany of these qualities?"
    },
    {
        "index": 30,
        "start_time": 90045,
        "end_time": 93097,
        "text": "For crabs and cuttlefish, \nthe answer is no."
    },
    {
        "index": 31,
        "start_time": 93097,
        "end_time": 96313,
        "text": "They don&#39;t combine their signals \nin creative ways."
    },
    {
        "index": 32,
        "start_time": 96313,
        "end_time": 99747,
        "text": "Those signals also don&#39;t have to be \nin a grammatical order,"
    },
    {
        "index": 33,
        "start_time": 99747,
        "end_time": 102704,
        "text": "and they only communicate \ncurrent conditions,"
    },
    {
        "index": 34,
        "start_time": 102704,
        "end_time": 106175,
        "text": "like, &quot;I am healthy,&quot; \nor &quot;I am poisonous.&quot;"
    },
    {
        "index": 35,
        "start_time": 106175,
        "end_time": 110447,
        "text": "But some animals actually do display\nsome of these properties."
    },
    {
        "index": 36,
        "start_time": 110447,
        "end_time": 115558,
        "text": "Bees use the moves, angle, duration,\nand intensity of their waggle dance"
    },
    {
        "index": 37,
        "start_time": 115558,
        "end_time": 119694,
        "text": "to describe the location and richness\nof a food source."
    },
    {
        "index": 38,
        "start_time": 119694,
        "end_time": 121920,
        "text": "That source is outside the hive,"
    },
    {
        "index": 39,
        "start_time": 121920,
        "end_time": 125190,
        "text": "so they exhibit the property \nof displacement."
    },
    {
        "index": 40,
        "start_time": 125190,
        "end_time": 128408,
        "text": "They share that language trait\nwith prairie dogs,"
    },
    {
        "index": 41,
        "start_time": 128408,
        "end_time": 130494,
        "text": "which live in towns of thousands,"
    },
    {
        "index": 42,
        "start_time": 130494,
        "end_time": 136156,
        "text": "and are hunted by coyotes, hawks,\nbadgers, snakes, and humans."
    },
    {
        "index": 43,
        "start_time": 136156,
        "end_time": 140617,
        "text": "Their alarms calls indicate\nthe predator&#39;s size, shape, speed,"
    },
    {
        "index": 44,
        "start_time": 140617,
        "end_time": 144832,
        "text": "and, even for human predators,\nwhat the person is wearing"
    },
    {
        "index": 45,
        "start_time": 144832,
        "end_time": 147593,
        "text": "and if he&#39;s carrying a gun."
    },
    {
        "index": 46,
        "start_time": 147593,
        "end_time": 151765,
        "text": "Great apes, like chimps and gorillas,\nare great communicators, too."
    },
    {
        "index": 47,
        "start_time": 151765,
        "end_time": 154656,
        "text": "Some have even learned \na modified sign language."
    },
    {
        "index": 48,
        "start_time": 154656,
        "end_time": 158513,
        "text": "A chimpanzee named Washoe\ndemonstrated discreteness"
    },
    {
        "index": 49,
        "start_time": 158513,
        "end_time": 162118,
        "text": "by combining multiple signs\ninto original phrases,"
    },
    {
        "index": 50,
        "start_time": 162118,
        "end_time": 164422,
        "text": "like, &quot;Please open. Hurry.&quot;"
    },
    {
        "index": 51,
        "start_time": 164422,
        "end_time": 168558,
        "text": "Coco, a female gorilla who understands\nmore than 1000 signs,"
    },
    {
        "index": 52,
        "start_time": 168558,
        "end_time": 171736,
        "text": "and around 2000 words of spoken English"
    },
    {
        "index": 53,
        "start_time": 171736,
        "end_time": 174892,
        "text": "referred to a beloved kitten \nthat had died."
    },
    {
        "index": 54,
        "start_time": 174892,
        "end_time": 177514,
        "text": "In doing so, she displayed displacement,"
    },
    {
        "index": 55,
        "start_time": 177514,
        "end_time": 180517,
        "text": "though it&#39;s worth noting that the apes\nin both of these examples"
    },
    {
        "index": 56,
        "start_time": 180517,
        "end_time": 183502,
        "text": "were using a human communication system,"
    },
    {
        "index": 57,
        "start_time": 183502,
        "end_time": 186648,
        "text": "not one that appeared \nnaturally in the wild."
    },
    {
        "index": 58,
        "start_time": 186648,
        "end_time": 190367,
        "text": "There are many other examples\nof sophisticated animal communication,"
    },
    {
        "index": 59,
        "start_time": 190367,
        "end_time": 191716,
        "text": "such as in dolphins,"
    },
    {
        "index": 60,
        "start_time": 191716,
        "end_time": 197442,
        "text": "which use whistles to identify age, \nlocation, names, and gender."
    },
    {
        "index": 61,
        "start_time": 197442,
        "end_time": 199370,
        "text": "They can also understand some grammar"
    },
    {
        "index": 62,
        "start_time": 199370,
        "end_time": 203481,
        "text": "in a gestural language researchers use\nto communicate with them."
    },
    {
        "index": 63,
        "start_time": 203481,
        "end_time": 208347,
        "text": "However, grammar is not seen \nin the dolphin&#39;s natural communication."
    },
    {
        "index": 64,
        "start_time": 208347,
        "end_time": 210004,
        "text": "While these communication systems"
    },
    {
        "index": 65,
        "start_time": 210004,
        "end_time": 213439,
        "text": "may have some of the qualities \nof language we&#39;ve identified,"
    },
    {
        "index": 66,
        "start_time": 213439,
        "end_time": 215913,
        "text": "none display all four."
    },
    {
        "index": 67,
        "start_time": 215913,
        "end_time": 220002,
        "text": "Even Washoe and Coco&#39;s impressive \nabilities are still outpaced"
    },
    {
        "index": 68,
        "start_time": 220002,
        "end_time": 223890,
        "text": "by the language skills \nof most three-year-old humans."
    },
    {
        "index": 69,
        "start_time": 223890,
        "end_time": 227163,
        "text": "And animals&#39; topics of conversation\nare usually limited."
    },
    {
        "index": 70,
        "start_time": 227163,
        "end_time": 228672,
        "text": "Bees talk about food,"
    },
    {
        "index": 71,
        "start_time": 228672,
        "end_time": 230799,
        "text": "prairie dogs talk about predators,"
    },
    {
        "index": 72,
        "start_time": 230799,
        "end_time": 233911,
        "text": "and crabs talk about themselves."
    },
    {
        "index": 73,
        "start_time": 233911,
        "end_time": 236196,
        "text": "Human language stands alone"
    },
    {
        "index": 74,
        "start_time": 236196,
        "end_time": 240051,
        "text": "due to the powerful combination\nof grammar and productivity,"
    },
    {
        "index": 75,
        "start_time": 240051,
        "end_time": 243305,
        "text": "on top of discreteness and displacement."
    },
    {
        "index": 76,
        "start_time": 243305,
        "end_time": 245880,
        "text": "The human brain can take \na finite number of elements"
    },
    {
        "index": 77,
        "start_time": 245880,
        "end_time": 248864,
        "text": "and create an infinite number of messages."
    },
    {
        "index": 78,
        "start_time": 248864,
        "end_time": 251561,
        "text": "We can craft and understand \ncomplex sentences,"
    },
    {
        "index": 79,
        "start_time": 251561,
        "end_time": 255004,
        "text": "as well as words that have never\nbeen spoken before."
    },
    {
        "index": 80,
        "start_time": 255004,
        "end_time": 258576,
        "text": "We can use language to communicate\nabout an endless range of subjects,"
    },
    {
        "index": 81,
        "start_time": 258576,
        "end_time": 260594,
        "text": "talk about imaginary things,"
    },
    {
        "index": 82,
        "start_time": 260594,
        "end_time": 262750,
        "text": "and even lie."
    },
    {
        "index": 83,
        "start_time": 262750,
        "end_time": 267096,
        "text": "Research continues to reveal more\nand more about animal communication."
    },
    {
        "index": 84,
        "start_time": 267096,
        "end_time": 270783,
        "text": "It may turn out that human language\nand animal communication"
    },
    {
        "index": 85,
        "start_time": 270783,
        "end_time": 274449,
        "text": "aren&#39;t entirely different\nbut exist on a continuum."
    },
    {
        "index": 86,
        "start_time": 274449,
        "end_time": 276921,
        "text": "After all, we are all animals."
    }
]